	(554, 'Public works Department', 4, 2216, 'Integration of Public Health with Basic Nursing Curriculum', 'The objective is to incorporate public health concepts and practices into core nursing courses. This integration aims to better prepare nurses to address the broader determinants of health and improve population health outcomes'),
	(555, 'Public works Department', 4, 2300, 'Direction and Administration (Proportionate Share of Establishment Transferred from Public Works for Demand No. 67-2059)', 'The scheme involves administrative and managerial functions essential for overseeing public works projects, ensuring effective governance.'),
