	(621, 'Public works Department', 4, 6464, 'Payment of Interest on Loan Taken by C.G.R.I.D.C.L. for Construction Work', 'The scheme aligns with goal 9. This goal emphasizes building resilient infrastructure and sustainable industrialization, which this scheme supports by financing construction projects through loan repayments, thus enabling continued infrastructure development.'),
