	(644, 'Public works Department', 4, 7609, 'Establishment Expenditure of ADB Assisted Chhattisgarh Road Development Project', 'The scheme seeks to boost infrastructure facility.'),
	(645, 'Public works Department', 4, 7808, 'Maintenance of Jaitkhamb in Giroudpuri', 'Maintaining cultural or community structures like Jaitkhamb supports local heritage preservation and contributes to the sustainable development of community spaces and settlements'),
	(646, 'Public works Department', 4, 7818, 'E.P.C. (Engineering Procurement and Construction)', 'The scheme seeks to boost construction facility.'),
	(647, 'Public works Department', 4, 7827, 'For Building Construction of District Emergency Operation Center', 'The objective is to ensure effective disaster response. '),
	(648, 'Public works Department', 4, 7922, 'Chhattisgarh State Road Development Sector Project Phase - III', 'This project focuses on the development, rehabilitation, and strengthening of state roads to improve connectivity, remove capacity bottlenecks, and support socio-economic development by linking rural areas with growth centers. The scheme also emphasizes institutional strengthening and road asset management, promoting sustainable infrastructure and inclusive industrialization'),
	(649, 'Public works Department', 4, 794, 'Maintenance of Art and Culture Buildings', 'The scheme aligns with goal 11, specifically Target 11.4, which aims to protect and safeguard the world’s cultural and natural heritage. Preserving cultural buildings supports social cohesion, local identity, sustainable tourism, and community well-being, all crucial aspects of sustainable urban development.'),
	(650, 'Public works Department', 4, 7976, 'Jawahar Setu Yojana', 'The scheme aligns with goal 9. This scheme focuses on the construction and maintenance of bridges and related infrastructure to improve connectivity, safety, and accessibility on national highways. It supports resilient infrastructure development, reduces travel time, and enhances transport efficiency, directly contributing to sustainable industrialization and infrastructure growth.'),
	(651, 'Public works Department', 4, 7977, 'Roads of Urban Area', 'The scheme seeks to boost construction facility.'),
