	(669, 'Public works Department', 4, 9269, 'Renovation and Replacement of Machines', 'The Renovation and Replacement of Machines scheme aligns primarily with goal 9, as it promotes upgrading and modernizing machinery to foster sustainable industrialization and enhance innovation. It also relates to goal 8: Decent Work and Economic Growth by supporting productivity improvements and sustainable economic activities through technological advancement and infrastructure modernization.'),
	(670, 'Public works Department', 4, 9840, 'Construction of Buildings for Educational Institutions', 'The objective of constructing buildings for educational institutions is to create safe, functional, and inspiring spaces that support effective learning and community engagement. '),
