	(710, 'School Education Department', 17, 6615, 'Pradhan Mantri Poshan Shakti Nirman Yojana', 'The Pradhan Mantri Kaushal Vikas Yojana (PMKVY) is a flagship scheme of the Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship (MSDE). The objective of this skill certification program is to enable a large number of Indian youth to acquire industry-relevant skill training, thereby helping them secure better livelihoods'),
	(711, 'School Education Department', 17, 6664, 'PM SHRI Scheme', 'The main objective of PM SHRI Yojana is to develop model schools across the country, which provide quality education in accordance with the principles of National Education Policy 22. The scheme focuses on developing schools as centres of excellence and preparing students for the future.   '),
	(712, 'School Education Department', 17, 6665, 'Nav Bharat Literacy Program', 'The Nav Bharat Literacy Program, also known as ULLAS (Understanding Lifelong Learning for All in Society), aims to achieve 1% literacy. '),
	(713, 'School Education Department', 17, 6690, 'National Teacher Training Institute', 'The primary objective of a National Teacher Training Institute is to enhance the quality of education by improving the skills and knowledge of teachers. This is achieved through various training programs, research activities, and the development of educational resources.  '),
	(714, 'School Education Department', 17, 67, 'English Education Study Institute', 'The objective is to equip students with the necessary skills and knowledge to effectively use the English language, both for academic and professional purposes, and to foster a deeper understanding and appreciation of english literature. '),
	(715, 'School Education Department', 17, 6744, 'EduSat Program', 'The primary objective of the EDUSAT program was to facilitate distance education through satellite technology, specifically designed to meet the needs of the educational sector.'),
	(716, 'School Education Department', 17, 6795, 'Typing Board Formation', 'The Typing Board typically focuses on skill development, vocational training, and promoting digital literacy, which contribute to inclusive and equitable quality education.'),
	(717, 'School Education Department', 17, 6796, 'Conducting National Examinations', 'The main objective of conducting national examinations is to assess candidates\' competency for admissions, recruitment, or other purposes, while also contributing to educational research and development. '),
	(718, 'School Education Department', 17, 6889, 'Chief Minister Knowledge Promotion Scheme', 'The primary objective of a CMKPS would be to enhance the knowledge and skills of a specific target group within the state. This could include students, unemployed youth, farmers, women, or marginalized communities.'),
	(719, 'School Education Department', 17, 6943, 'State literacy program', 'The scheme seeks to boost literacy.'),
	(720, 'School Education Department', 17, 6944, 'library plan', 'The scheme seeks to boost education.'),
	(721, 'School Education Department', 17, 7015, 'Special Backward Caste Ashram', 'The objective of a Special Backward Caste Ashram is to provide educational and residential support to students from specific backward castes who may face social and economic challenges. These ashrams aim to bridge the educational gap and promote overall development by offering free accommodation, meals, and education, particularly for those who might otherwise lack access to these opportunities. '),
	(722, 'School Education Department', 17, 7363, 'Youth Career Building Scheme', 'The "Yuva Career Nirman Yojana" aims to provide free coaching, accommodation, food, and other support to economically weaker students, particularly those from Scheduled Tribes, Scheduled Castes, and Other Backward Classes, for competitive exams like NEET, CLAT, NDA, and PAT. '),
	(723, 'School Education Department', 17, 7367, 'Model School', 'The Model School Scheme aims to establish high-quality senior secondary schools.'),
	(724, 'School Education Department', 17, 761, 'Girl Education Campus', 'The objective is to provide a safe and supportive environment that empowers girls to pursue their education. '),
	(725, 'School Education Department', 17, 7657, 'Establishment of Science Center', 'To portray the growth of science and technology and their applications in industry and human welfare, with a view to develop scientific attitude and temper and to create, inculcate and sustain a general awareness amongst the people.'),
	(726, 'School Education Department', 17, 7761, 'Teacher\'s Salary', 'Providing fair and adequate compensation to teachers is essential for attracting, retaining, and motivating qualified educators, which directly supports the goal of delivering inclusive and equitable quality education'),
	(727, 'School Education Department', 17, 7765, 'Chief Minister Amrit Yojana', 'The objective of the scheme is to improve access of BPL families to quality medical and surgical care for the treatment of identified diseases involving hospitalization, surgeries and therapies through an em panel network of health care providers'),
	(728, 'School Education Department', 17, 7840, 'Divisional Office', 'The scheme aligns with goal 16. The scheme involves establishing and maintaining administrative offices at the divisional level, which supports building effective, accountable, and inclusive institutions critical for good governance and public service delivery. Strong institutional frameworks at divisional and local levels contribute to the overall goal of peace, justice, and effective governance'),
	(729, 'School Education Department', 17, 7841, 'Central Library', 'The scheme seeks to boost education through providing the facility of library.'),
	(730, 'School Education Department', 17, 7979, 'holistic education', 'The main objective of Samagra Shiksha is to provide quality education to all children from pre-school to class 12 . It aims to ensure equity and inclusion in education, improve the quality of education, and enhance student learning outcomes. '),
	(731, 'School Education Department', 17, 8050, 'Scholarships', 'The main objective of scholarships is to provide financial assistance to students, enabling them to pursue their educational goals.'),
	(732, 'School Education Department', 17, 8403, 'Salary and Allowancesfor Teachers ', 'Grant-in-aid is a system of financial assistance given to all private educational institutions which agree to submit to inspection by government and rules prescribed for grant-in-aid.'),
	(733, 'School Education Department', 17, 8647, 'Promotion of STEM education', 'The objective of expanding science and mathematics education is to enhance students\' understanding and engagement with these subjects, fostering critical thinking, problem-solving skills, and a lifelong love for learning in STEM fields.  '),
