	(970, 'Food, Civil Supplies Department ', NULL, 9993, 'Subsidy for Distribution of Iodised Salt at Concessional Rate', 'The scheme aims to provide subsidized salt to beneficiaries, ensuring affordability and nutrition intake for economically weaker sections.'),
