	(1081, 'Public Health and Engineering Department', NULL, 6434, 'Water Supply scheme for Indian Institute of Technology Bhilai', 'The water supply scheme for the Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Bhilai involves developing a comprehensive water management system for the new campus near Bhilai, Chhattisgarh. This includes a water supply network, storm water network, and a wastewater treatment plant. The scheme is part of the larger development plan for the campus, which is being developed in phases. '),
