	(1422, 'Animal Husbandry Department', NULL, 7212, 'Comprehensive Dairy Development Scheme', 'The scheme aligns with the following two Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs): Goal 1: – By supporting dairy farmers, improving market access, income generation, and rural livelihoods, the scheme plays a crucial role in poverty reduction. Goal 2: – The scheme contributes significantly to food security and improved nutrition by increasing milk production and availability, addressing nutritional needs of vulnerable groups.'),
	(1423, 'Capacity Building,Technical Education & Employment Department ', NULL, 515, 'Construction of Buildings for Engineering / Technical Colleges and Institutions', 'The objective is to provide suitable infrastructure for delivering high-quality technical education and training. This includes creating spaces for classrooms, laboratories, workshops, research centers, administrative offices, and student/faculty amenities, all designed to support effective teaching, learning, and research activities in various engineering and technology disciplines. '),
