	(1448, 'Finance Department', NULL, 7565, 'Chhattisgarh Growth and Stability Fund', 'The scheme aligns primarily with goal 8. The fund supports sustainable economic growth by providing financial stability and growth support to various sectors, fostering employment and economic development. It also aligns with goal 1 by contributing to poverty alleviation through economic growth and livelihood support initiatives in the state.'),
