	(1486, 'Local Government Department', NULL, 7109, 'Prime Minister E Bus Service', 'The PM e-Bus Sewa scheme, also known as PM e-Drive, aims to enhance urban public transportation by deploying 1, electric buses across India, with a focus on cities lacking organized bus services. The scheme\'s primary objectives are to strengthen urban transport infrastructure, promote cleaner and efficient transport, and generate employment opportunities, particularly for the youth. It also seeks to encourage the adoption of electric vehicles and develop a robust EV ecosystem. '),
