	(1498, 'Public Health and Engineering Department', NULL, 191, 'Construction of Buildings for tourism under other transport and communication services', 'The objective of constructing buildings for tourism under "other transport and communication services" is to create facilities that support and enhance the tourism experience while also contributing to the overall transportation and communication infrastructure. This includes building structures like tourist information centers, transportation hubs with amenities, and communication facilities to improve accessibility and information flow for tourists. '),
	(1499, 'Public Health and Engineering Department', NULL, 6860, 'Champa water supply scheme', 'The scheme is part of the larger Jal Jeevan Mission (JJM), which aims to ensure every rural household has a functional tap connection. This involves not just providing access to water but also ensuring its quality and sustainability. '),
